##  Benefits

We offer a range of benefits to help provide holistic support for your work
life, whatever your circumstances. As a QBE employee you will have access to
and benefit from:

‘Hybrid Working’ – a mix of working from home and in the office to enhance
your work/life balance

Our ‘Thriving at our Best’ wellbeing program, including free holistic
wellbeing coaching, nutritional, confidential counselling, financial and legal
advice

12 weeks’ gender-equal flexible leave for all new parents, including paid
super

The ability to maximise retirement savings through voluntary super
contributions and company matching

Income protection insurance & reimbursed Death and Total Permanent Disability
insurance premiums

Additional leave and support through QBE’s Family Domestic Violence First
Responder Network

Discounts on insurance products, car hire, hotels, goods and services
including benefits through our various sports and arts sponsorship partners

